# 🎒 Campus Lost & Found Portal

A simple web application for students to post and find lost or found items inside the campus.

---

## 🚀 Features

- User Registration & Login
- Add Lost / Found Items
- Upload Item Images
- Search Items
- Claim Lost Items
- Admin Panel
- Manage Users & Items

---

## 🛠 Technologies Used

### Frontend
- HTML
- CSS
- Bootstrap
- JavaScript

### Backend
- Node.js
- Express.js

### Database
- MongoDB

### Other Packages
- Multer
- CORS

---

