## How to run Project

Clone Repository
git clone https://github.com/YTManish/Campus-Lost-Found-Portal.git

# Install packages
cd backend
npm install

# Start Server
node server.js

# Next open Frontend Register.html / Login.html

## Mongo DB Connection
mongodb://127.0.0.1:27017/lostfound
use this connetion

Database and collections will be created automatically.

#Collections used:
users
items

## For admin user 
Go to admin and in users collection, go to Add Data and paste this admin id

{
  "name": "Admin",
  "contact": "9999999999",
  "department": "Admin",
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin",
  "role": "admin"
}

Username and pasword mentioned here in id.
